1
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:41,680
Your Majesty.

2
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:44,810
I am fine.

3
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:51,960
Are you all right?

4
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,020
You little wretch!

5
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:56,520
You slack off and steal food!

6
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:57,240
Stop!

7
00:01:58,520 --> 00:02:00,980
His Majesty is here. Do not be presumptuous.

8
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,920
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

9
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,850
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

10
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,000
Xie Yan

11
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:19,290
is the son of Xie Chen, the former Minister of War.

12
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,579
The Xie family.

13
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,680
The Xie family disappeared overnight back then.

14
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,680
It became a sensational case throughout the capital.

15
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,840
Although I was far away at the border,

16
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,240
I heard a little about it.

17
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,770
This was torn from his clothes.

18
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:31,200
They belong to this organization

19
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:33,060
and obey the command of the token.

20
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,290
In this life.

21
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,640
With these two clues,

22
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,720
Li Yunxi should be able to find out

23
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:39,640
who they are.

24
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,620
Does it look familiar?

25
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,800
It looks a lot like

26
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,000
the Xuanniao Totem.

27
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:46,170
However,

28
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,320
this is a fake.

29
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,200
It differs slightly from the real Xuanniao Totem

30
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:50,760
in the tail feathers.

31
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:53,040
Not only do you know about the Xuanniao Tribe,

32
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:54,970
but you can even see these details.

33
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,040
I have sharp eyes.

34
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,320
Su Kuang,

35
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,760
you told me that in our last life.

36
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,280
Where is Consort Xue?

37
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,040
Let her in.

38
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,210
Consort Xue,

39
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,040
why were you there?

40
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,720
I left the palace to visit my family,

41
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:12,840
but I got lost on my way back.

42
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,120
Your Majesty,

43
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:19,200
I found this token in Feixue Hall.

44
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:29,079
The assassins take orders from this token.

45
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,700
What do you have to say?

46
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:32,720
I...

47
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:36,880
Where did this token come from?

48
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:42,240
A mysterious man in a mask gave it to me.

49
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,200
With this command token,

50
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:52,280
can I really kill the one I want dead?

51
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,079
Of course.

52
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,920
How audacious!

53
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,520
You dare to publicly murder the Empress.

54
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,320
Your Majesty.

55
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:02,520
I was blinded by obsession for a moment

56
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,120
and committed a grave error.

57
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,840
Please spare me this time.

58
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,300
Consort Xue doesn't seem to be lying.

59
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,400
In that case,

60
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,960
someone else wants to kill my father and me.

61
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:16,540
This mysterious man is the mastermind behind everything.

62
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:17,839
Your Majesty,

63
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,690
please give me a chance to atone for my crimes.

64
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,800
What kind of mask?

65
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,200
It was a

66
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,640
terrifying ghost mask.

67
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,920
A ghost mask.

68
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:34,810
Could it be the person I saw at the Xiao residence?

69
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,680
Who exactly is behind that ghost mask?

70
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,600
I do not know.

71
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,880
He only shows himself in a mask.

72
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,560
You need not interfere in this matter, Empress.

73
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,960
I will investigate it myself.

74
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:43,490
Su Kuang.

75
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:46,760
Pass on my order. Depose Consort Xue.

76
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:47,680
Your Majesty.

77
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,200
Do you really intend to depose me?

78
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:58,659
She actually dares to threaten Li Yunxi.

79
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,360
Does she have something on you?

80
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,320
I don't.

81
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:13,560
Does she really have something on Li Yunxi?

82
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:18,890
Consort Xue is confined to Feixue Palace.

83
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:20,560
Without my decree,

84
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:23,370
she is not to take a single step out.

85
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,330
There must be something fishy about this.

86
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,600
This must be the truth

87
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,330
that Li Yunxi wouldn't tell me.

88
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,120
Two years ago,

89
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,840
I rushed back from the border

90
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:40,440
to keep my engagement with Li Yunxi.

91
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,120
But I suddenly learned...

92
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:46,880
Li Yunxi wants to take Liu Mianmian as a concubine.

93
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,240
Who is she?

94
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,100
Since I gave you the Phoenix Seal,

95
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,760
I will keep my promise

96
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,210
and make you my Empress.

97
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,730
As for Mianmian,

98
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:20,120
she will enter the harem with you

99
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,240
as my favored consort.

100
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,000
Li Yunxi.

101
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,940
What exactly is happening

102
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:39,159
that makes you bear this in silence?

103
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:41,320
And why can't we face it together?

104
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,520
When Father was alive,

105
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:50,800
he founded the Xuanniao Department to eliminate dissidents

106
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,060
and assassinated countless officials.

107
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:55,960
Now the descendants of the victims have appeared.

108
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:58,020
They use the same methods against me.

109
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,760
I suppose it's retribution.

110
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,320
In this world,

111
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:05,440
those who can quietly find the descendants of guilty officials

112
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,600
and unite them

113
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:07,920
are few.

114
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,040
Xiao Rushan.

115
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:14,200
You don't want the Empress to investigate this matter.

116
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:16,320
Isn't it because you've made up your mind,

117
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:18,040
fearing that if Her Highness learns the truth,

118
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:20,920
she'll be torn between you and the General?

119
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:22,600
Use the Xuanniao Ministry's list

120
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:25,200
of assassinated ministers to follow the clues

121
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,160
and arrest those assassins.

122
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,200
Between you and Li Yunxi,

123
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,210
what exactly is the secret?

124
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,560
Your Highness,

125
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,040
do you really want to know?

126
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,800
You used threats to get all this.

127
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,810
Are you truly happy?

128
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:04,560
But the one who actually forbade me from telling you is His Majesty.

129
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,360
Look at him.

130
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:07,440
He's usually so aloof.

131
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,960
But whenever this is mentioned,

132
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,820
even his greatest rage subsides.

133
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,520
Is His Majesty happy?

134
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,420
What is it exactly?

135
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,720
But I won't tell you even if I die.

136
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,160
Because once I tell the truth,

137
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,400
I won't have any leverage left,

138
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:36,559
and I'll even lose everything I have now.

139
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,440
Who is Ghost Face?

140
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,330
Naturally, he is His Majesty's enemy.

141
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:45,680
If only for the sake of the baby,

142
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,620
please eat something.

143
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,800
How do you know?

144
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,420
Take it or leave it.

145
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,410
You were willing to save me that day

146
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,780
only for the sake of

147
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:01,960
His Majesty's child.

148
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:05,960
You are lucky.

149
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,200
With this child,

150
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:10,250
you have a bond with him.

151
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,200
I want to see His Majesty.

152
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,160
If you ask him to come,

153
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,120
He will definitely come.

154
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,680
I have never touched you.

155
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:37,010
Who exactly is the child's father?

156
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:38,200
Your Majesty.

157
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,640
You haven't told the truth about that matter

158
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,960
to the Empress yet.

159
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,100
I can send you out of the palace

160
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,240
to be with the child's father.

161
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:52,570
Your Majesty doesn't care about me at all,

162
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:55,440
so you don't care about my betrayal.

163
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,720
I can save you some face,

164
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,600
but I hope you use your brain.

165
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:02,050
Since you know I don't care,

166
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:03,940
stop lingering in the palace.

167
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,720
I have nowhere else to go.

168
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,760
I just want to stay in the palace,

169
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:13,440
stay in Feixue Hall,

170
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,600
and be your Consort Xue.

171
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:19,440
Fine.

172
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:21,760
Then from today on,

173
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:23,760
Feixue Hall

174
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:26,520
is your Cold Palace.

175
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

176
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:31,610
Actually, what's the difference between us?

177
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:34,760
We both love someone so desperately.

178
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:45,640
I knew Liu Mianmian would get pregnant in my last life.

179
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:47,240
But now that it's happening,

180
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,490
I still get jealous.

181
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:57,560
It's late.

182
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:58,970
No drinking.

183
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:10,280
Isn't your Consort Xue pregnant?

184
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,760
Why did you still confine her?

185
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:13,160
Consort Xue is pregnant.

186
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:16,360
You aren't making a scene, getting angry, or jealous?

187
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,980
She is your favorite consort.

188
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:19,880
Her pregnancy

189
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,040
is a joyous occasion.

190
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,680
You don't mean that.

191
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:34,160
Get out.

192
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,200
The child isn't mine.

193
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:38,880
What?

194
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,560
It really isn't mine.

195
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,010
I never touched her.

196
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,280
She cheated on me.

197
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:50,800
How can you say that

198
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,680
so calmly?

199
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,240
Do I look calm?

200
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,970
But I swear to God it's true.

201
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:01,680
No.

202
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,680
How is that possible?

203
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:11,400
If I have kids,

204
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,640
it'll only be with you.

205
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,240
Your Majesty.

206
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:32,360
I once thought you were the light of my life,

207
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,660
always chasing after you.

208
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,200
Sadly,

209
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:40,560
it was all just my delusion.

210
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,520
Empress.

211
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:46,680
I hope you like

212
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:50,560
this final gift from me.

213
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:57,280
Consort Xue.

214
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:02,680
Empress.

215
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:06,200
I'll haunt you even after death.
